title: Session Comparison Exception

milestone.description: Enhancements and bug fixes expected to be included in the next main release.

body:
Per this User Group thread: https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/zaproxy-users/mXevo4pguWg

Using current code via Eclipse.

I did a quick session that just proxied example.org and saved. Created a new session just proxying scanme.nmap.org and then example.org, I then selected compare vs the original session. The exception below came up in the eclipse console.

